reviews.review_text: - A pretty good show, great recording!

Whoa To my ears, this source sounds a bit better than the other SBDs, even the Charlie Miller. '71 did not have the best SBDs due to Bear's departure to the pokey for his hobbies. 

4-star performance at a classic venue.
